OL,3,CBlast at explosive storage building
OL,4,Ckills 45 in Myanmar, reports say
OL,6,FA blast at a building in northeastern
OL,7,FMyanmar that was reportedly storing
OL,8,Fexplosives for mining has killed more
OL,9,Fthan 45 people, according to rescue
OL,10,Fworkers and independent media reports.
OL,12,FAbout 70 other people were injured in
OL,13,Fthe explosion that took place around
OL,14,Fnoon in the village of Kaungtup, in
OL,15,FNamhkam township.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
