OL,3,CBlast at explosive storage building
OL,4,Ckills 45 in Myanmar, reports say
OL,6,FThe area, located about 2 miles south
OL,7,Fof the Chinese border, is under the
OL,8,Fcontrol of the Ta'ang National
OL,9,FLiberation Army, an ethnic armed group
OL,10,Fwhich has engaged in sporadic fighting
OL,11,Fagainst Myanmar's central government.
OL,13,FA rescue worker who rushed to the site
OL,14,Fof the blast told The Associated Press
OL,15,Fthat 46 bodies, including six
OL,16,Fchildren, had been recovered by Sunday
OL,17,Fevening and taken for cremation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
