CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780297676
OL,3,CBlast at explosive storage building
OL,4,Ckills 45 in Myanmar, reports say
OL,6,FThe rescuer, who spoke on condition of
OL,7,Fanonymity for security reasons, said
OL,8,F74 injured people had been transported
OL,9,Fto the township hospital and rescue
OL,10,Foperations were continuing.
OL,12,FAnother rescuer in Namhkam, who also
OL,13,Fspoke on condition of anonymity, said
OL,14,Fabout 40 people were killed and more
OL,15,Fthan 100 houses near the blast site
OL,16,Fwere damaged.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
