OL,3,CBlast at explosive storage building
OL,4,Ckills 45 in Myanmar, reports say
OL,6,FMyanmar media outlets, including Shan
OL,7,FState's online Shwe Phee Myay news
OL,8,Fagency, reported death tolls ranging
OL,9,Ffrom 50 to 55. They published photos
OL,10,Fand videos showing smoke from the
OL,11,Fexplosion and damaged buildings and
OL,12,Fdebris in its aftermath.
OL,14,FChinese state broadcaster CCTV
OL,15,Freported the explosion caused multiple
OL,16,Fdeaths and injuries, with many
OL,17,Fresidential houses being severely
OL,18,Fdamaged, but did not give figures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
