OL,3,CBlast at explosive storage building
OL,4,Ckills 45 in Myanmar, reports say
OL,6,FIt said that according to preliminary
OL,7,Finvestigations, the blast occurred at
OL,8,Fa site where large quantities of
OL,9,Fexplosives used for mining operations
OL,10,Fwere stored.
OL,12,FLocal authorities are currently
OL,13,Fproviding relief, medical care and
OL,14,Fresettlement assistance to affected
OL,15,Fresidents, said the report.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
