OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780297676
OL,3,CBlast at explosive storage building
OL,4,Ckills 45 in Myanmar, reports say
OL,6,FThe Ta'ang National Liberation Army,
OL,7,For TNLA, said in a statement released
OL,8,Fon its Telegram channel that gelignite
OL,9,Fhad been stored by the group's
OL,10,Feconomic department for use in mining
OL,11,Fand stone quarrying sites, and that an
OL,12,Finvestigation into the cause of the
OL,13,Fexplosion is underway.
OL,15,FGelignite is widely used in mining and
OL,16,Frock blasting, but can become highly
OL,17,Funstable over time and if poorly
OL,18,Fstored.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
