OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780297676
OL,3,CBlast at explosive storage building
OL,4,Ckills 45 in Myanmar, reports say
OL,6,FThe Ta'ang National Liberation Army,
OL,7,For TNLA, is a member of the rebel
OL,8,FThree Brotherhood Alliance, and has
OL,9,Fcontrolled the Namhkam area since it
OL,10,Fand its allies launched a major
OL,11,Foffensive against the military in
OL,12,Fnortheastern Myanmar in late 2023.
OL,14,FThe alliance members and other ethnic
OL,15,Farmed groups have long fought for
OL,16,Fincreased autonomy.
OL,18,FThe TNLA signed a ceasefire with
OL,19,FMyanmar's military following China-
OL,20,Fmediated talks in October last year,
OL,21,Fbut relations remain tense.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
