OL,3,CBlast at explosive storage building
OL,4,Ckills 45 in Myanmar, reports say
OL,6,FMyanmar has been in turmoil since the
OL,7,Farmy seized power from the elected
OL,8,Fgovernment of Aung San Suu Kyi on
OL,9,FFebruary 1, 2021, triggering
OL,10,Fwidespread popular opposition.
OL,12,FAfter peaceful demonstrations were put
OL,13,Fdown with lethal force, many opponents
OL,14,Fof military rule took up arms, and
OL,15,Flarge parts of the country are now
OL,16,Fembroiled in conflict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
